{"tid":682763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大參戰！ 對中國等地鋼材展開反傾銷調查","createTime":"2018-05-29T06:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T23:11:37.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"862bdc9d3461c7a9eb498949d500555a5ad7c1d4","tid":682763,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"加拿大參戰！ 對中國等地鋼材展開反傾銷調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2440603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2440603&d=eDwkGaQ54RoKqYAzRiZ3yBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0c0a5ddb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2440603&h=97c42164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2440603</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中美貿易摩擦看似稍稍舒緩，加拿大突然展開動作，宣布對中國、南韓和越南進口的鋼材展開調查，以確認是否有傾銷行為。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，加拿大國際貿易法庭（Canadian International Trade Tribunal，CITT）於28日表示，已調查上述國家進口到加拿大的「冷軋碳素鋼板（cold-reduced flat-rolled sheet products of carbon steel）」，是否損害了加拿大的鋼鐵工業。<br />\n<br />\nCITT指出，調查結果將於7月24日出爐，並在8月8日提供判斷理由。事實上，美國商務部上週已展開類似行動，美方發現原產地在中國的越南鋼鐵產品，逃避美國的反傾銷命令後，已對其徵收大量進口關稅。<br />\n<br />\n全球鋼鐵產業正面臨著產能過剩的困境，其中大部分過剩的產能來自中國，這影響並降低了鋼材的價格。"},{"pid":"21be85d5e64d2d314ed44a088dcfa79e0709c4d1","tid":682763,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"加拿大同英國就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國畀多少少錢咪又係跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要換埋個濕鳩左膠總統，加拿大人自求多福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f726583fe92ee95b5b353d28e992ac2fba956e4","tid":682763,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21be85d5e64d2d314ed44a088dcfa79e0709c4d1","tid":682763,"uid":143499,"like":0,"disli